<Content>Exceptional hotel experience!! We stayed at the ME for 4 days and I could not be happier with my choice!!First of all, the location was great, we walked to all the museums, Palacio Real, Plaza Mayor, etc. Its about a 5-10 minute walk anywhere you want to go in the city (with the exception of serrano st shopping which has is a short cab ride). Also, its right around the corner from Puerto Sol which is the hub of the city. Plaza Santa Ana, where the hotel is located, is where all the tapas bars/nightlife is and it seemed that there was always something going on day or night. A great place to people watch.The hotel itself was immaculate, very stylish and modern, and we loved coming back to our room after a long day of sight seeing. We had a deluxe inside room which was smaller than other hotels we have stayed in but the room was very well laid out, had one of the most comfortable beds we have slept in and a GREAT shower. The atmosphere of the hotel is very young, urban, sophisticated, and sexy, and the crowd the same. This really is one of in spots in Madrid. The restaurants and bars had great atmosphere, including the rooftop penthouse which had a great view and great crowd. Finally, I want to comment about service and say that it was ABSOLUTELY EXCEPTIONAL. Room Service, maid service, and wait staff were top notch, but we the level of attention of and service we received from the Concierge at the ME was really in a class of its own. We received great suggestions on restaurants, bars, shopping, etc. but one night, Lucas from the concierge staff helped turn a bad situation we experienced into a great one (of course one that neither he nor the hotel controlled). He went out of his way to help us, i have never had a concierge or hotel provide that level of service for myself or for anyone that I have ever know. We even got a hand written note from Lucas that night hoping that everything went well. I felt like one of the celebrities who was also staying at the hotel! This is my third visit to a ME hotel, and I can't wait until they open others. 
