<Content>Adored the Hotel and Location This Hotel has charm, character and an ideal location. Following a 14 day bus tour of Spain and Portugal staying at 4 and 5 star Hotels we stayed an additional 5 days at his Hotel. We found the breakfast at this Hotel to be the best of all hotels. The location is ideal for tourists who want to be within walking distance of all major sites. The Hotel staff was very friendly and the main desk staff speak very good english. We requested a large room with our reservation and received a beautiful 5th floor outside room with great views. There is noise from the square below most of the night, but after one or two nights, the joyful noises of the visitors are not offensive. We will definately return to this Hotel in the future. 
